    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the trim pieces. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear in high-traffic areas, and all major electronics are functional despite some minor cosmetic wear on the buttons. It runs and drives well, having received regular oil changes, but a prospective buyer should expect upcoming routine maintenance typical for a car of this vintage.",
