    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride with plenty of personality! This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road, showing some honest signs of use that tell the story of its journeys. It's a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for a car with character and a proven track record of getting the job done. Perfect for a driver who values practicality and a classic feel!",
